id: pm-pgew
title: Stabilize npx onboarding path for scoped pm package
description: "Fix GitHub issue #131 by making the first-command package execution path obvious and regression-tested for agents. Scope includes canonical npx docs, package/release smoke coverage, dependency/security triage, changelog validation, and temp-project dogfood."
type: Task
status: in_progress
priority: 1
